'''Google, Inc.''' ({{nasdaq|GOOG}} and {{lse|GGEA}}) is an [[United States|American]] [[public company|public corporation]] and [[search engine]], first [[Incorporation (business)|incorporated]] as a [[privately held company]] on [[7 September]] [[1998]].
